lines.text: Never dig up. Up is Hell.

[after shooting at the Starchaser]
That was just a warning shot. Reduce speed and prepare to be boarded.

[to Arthur]
Don't bother with the shields. That bot's about to get a laser-enema.

[to Silica]
Oh dear what have you done to me? I'm naked, put my ship back on you perverted fembot!
